---
import DetailLayout from '../layouts/DetailLayout.astro';
---
<DetailLayout title="Sketchware for Arduino">
  <section class="site-section" id="section-project-info">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row mb-5 align-items-center">
          <div class="col-md-6 pr-lg-5 mb-5 mb-lg-0">
            <!-- <img src="images/sketch_ino_main.gif" class="modal-img"> -->
            <div class="device-wrapper">
              <div class="device" data-device="Pixel" data-orientation="portrait" data-color="black">
                <div class="screen">
                  <img src="images/sketch_ino_main.gif" class="sketch-main-img">
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="section-heading">
              <h2>Sketchware for <strong>Arduino</strong></h2>
            </div>
            <p><span class="date"><span class="icon-calendar"></span> May 2019 - August 2019 </span></p>
            <p class="lead">블록형 프로그래밍 언어를 기반으로 아두이노를 제어하는 앱</p>
            <p class="mb-5">Eclipse CDT 기반 아두이노 라이브러리 헤더파일 파싱 구현
              <br>Physicaloid API 기반 아두이노 하드웨어 통신 및 시리얼 모니터 구현
              <br>Java · Spring Framework · MySQL · AWS 기반 프로젝트 공유 플랫폼 풀스택 개발
              <br>Google Play Store 출시 후 아두이노 프로그래밍 관련 앱 상위권 달성
            </p>
              <!-- <a href="#section-contact" class="btn btn-primary px-4 py-2 btn-sm smoothscroll">Go To Market</a> -->
            <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.sketchware.arduino">
              <img src="images/icons/google_play_badge.png" class="img-fluid google-play-badge">
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="site-section bg-light " id="section-works">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-12 mb-5">
            <div class="section-heading text-center">
              <h2>My <strong>Works</strong></h2>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="resume-item mb-4" data-toggle="modal" href="#portfolioModal1">
              <h3>Eclipse CDT 기반 아두이노 라이브러리 파싱 구현</h3>
              <span class="school">#eclipse #eclipse_cdt #ast</span>
            </div>
            <div class="resume-item mb-4" data-toggle="modal" href="#portfolioModal2">
              <h3>Physicaloid API 기반 아두이노 하드웨어 통신 구현</h3>
              <span class="school">#physicaloid #broadcast_receiver #usb_manager</span>
            </div>
            <div class="resume-item mb-4" data-toggle="modal" href="#portfolioModal3">
              <h3>시리얼 모니터 기능 개발</h3>
              <span class="school">#physicaloid #serial #baud_rate</span>
            </div>
            <div class="resume-item mb-4" data-toggle="modal" href="#portfolioModal4">
              <h3>프로젝트 공유 플랫폼 개발</h3>
              <span class="school">#full_stack #java #spring_framework #my_sql #my_batis</span>
            </div>
            <div class="resume-item mb-4" data-toggle="modal" href="#portfolioModal5">
              <h3>아두이노 예제 콘텐츠 기획 및 제작</h3>
              <span class="school">#youtube_android_player #web_view</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="portfolio-modal modal fade" id="portfolioModal1" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="modal-dialog">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <div class="close-modal" data-dismiss="modal">
            <div class="lr">
              <div class="rl"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
                <div class="modal-body">
                  <h3>Eclipse CDT 기반 아두이노 라이브러리 파싱 구현</h3><br>
                  <div id="carouselForModal1" class="carousel carousel-fade" data-ride="carousel">
                    <div class="carousel-inner">
                      <div class="carousel-item active">
                        <img class="parse-item" src="images/screenshots/ino/parse/1.png">
                      </div>
                      <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img class="parse-item" src="images/screenshots/ino/parse/2.png">
                      </div>
                      <div class="carousel-item">
