                      <div class="carousel-buttons">
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-left"></i>
                      </div>
                    </a>
                    <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselForModal1" role="button" data-slide="next">
                      <div class="carousel-buttons">
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i>
                      </div>
                    </a>
                  </div><br>
                  <div class="section-heading text-center">
                    <h3>주요 기능과 구현 내용</h3><br>
                  </div>
                  <div class="detail-desc">
                    <div class="detail-desc-items">
                      <h4>✓&nbsp Eclipse CDT(C/C++ Development Toolkit) 기반 아두이노 라이브러리 헤더파일 파싱 구현</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-desc-items">
